[x] NAME
[x] VERSION
[x] DESCRIPTION

[x] README (document-text)
[ ] VERSIONS (collection)
[ ] DEPENDENCIES (cube)
[ ] DEPENDENTS (database / duplicate)
[ ] STATS (chart-bar / chart-square-bar)
[ ] ACTIVITY (user-group / fingerprint)

[x] CONFIG
[x] CHECKSUM
[x] BUILD TOOLS
[x] OWNERS
[x] PUBLISHER
[x] KEYWORDS
[x] LINKS
[x] LICENSE

* Header
  * Name
  * Version
  * Description
* Main
  * Readme
  * Versions
  * Dependencies
  * Depenents
  * Stats
  * Activity
* Sidebar
  * This version
    * Checksum
    * Build tools
    * Publisher
  * Details
    * Links
    * License
    * Keywords
  * Config
  * Owners
-->

<div class="bg-gray-50 h-full">
  <main class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:flex md:items-center md:justify-between md:space-x-5 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          <%= @package.name %>
          <span class="text-sm font-normal"><%= @release.version %></span>
        </h1>
        <%= if description = @package.meta.description do %>
          <%= text_to_html(ViewHelpers.text_length(description, 300), insert_brs: false, attributes: [class: "text-sm font-medium text-gray-500"]) %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-6">
